🎯 Objective: Build a voice-enabled bank form with speech-to-text and text-to-speech features for seamless user interaction.

🟢 Phase 1: Planning & Research (Week 1)
   ✅ Define project scope and objectives
   ✅ Research speech recognition technologies (Google Speech API, Vosk, etc.)
   ✅ Plan frontend and backend architecture

🔵 Phase 2: Backend Development (Week 2-3)
   ✅ Set up Flask server
   ✅ Implement Speech-to-Text (Google Speech API)
   ✅ Implement Text-to-Speech (pyttsx3)
   ✅ Test API endpoints

🟠 Phase 3: Frontend Development (Week 4)
   ✅ Design UI (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
   ✅ Implement voice input and output on form fields
   ✅ Connect frontend to Flask API

🟡 Phase 4: Feature Enhancements (Week 5)
   ✅ Add multi-language support
   ✅ Implement error handling and correction
   ✅ Add confirmation prompts

🟣 Phase 5: Testing & Deployment (Week 6)
   ✅ Conduct unit testing on backend APIs
   ✅ Perform UI/UX testing for voice interactions
   ✅ Deploy project on a cloud platform (e.g., Heroku, AWS)


🏆 Final Deliverables
📄 Project Report: Documenting features, implementation, and challenges
📹 Demo Video: Showcasing project functionality
🔥 Live Demo: Running application
